                "invention-title": [
                    "Method for preparing liquid caustic soda and co-producing sulfur and hydrogen by using sodium sulfate",
                    "一种利用硫酸钠制备液碱联产硫和氢气的方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a method for preparing liquid caustic soda and co-producing sulfur and hydrogen by using sodium sulfate, and belongs to the technical field of electrolytic production of inorganic compounds or non-metals. Comprising the following steps: (1) mixing sodium sulfate and carbon to form a reaction precursor; (2) roasting the obtained reaction precursor in an inert atmosphere to convert sodium sulfate into sodium sulfide so as to obtain a roasted product; (3) putting the obtained roasted product into molten sodium chloride-potassium chloride mixed molten salt as an electrolyte, taking liquid metal bismuth as a cathode, and connecting an anode for electrolysis; a sodium-bismuth alloy is obtained at the cathode, and elemental sulfur is obtained at the anode; and (4) the obtained sodium-bismuth alloy reacts with water, so that sodium in the alloy reacts to obtain liquid caustic soda and hydrogen. The method is rich and low in raw material source and has the cost advantage; the process is simple and safe, no chlorine is generated, and the environmental pollution risk can be reduced; the method can be expanded to the aspect of active metal energy storage intermittent hydrogen production, is suitable for amplified production, and has large-scale production potential."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种利用硫酸钠制备液碱联产硫和氢气的方法，属于无机化合物或非金属的电解生产技术领域。包括如下步骤：(1)硫酸钠与炭混合形成反应前驱体；(2)所得反应前驱体于惰性气氛下经焙烧，使硫酸钠转化为硫化钠，得到焙烧产物；(3)将所得焙烧产物投入熔融态氯化钠‑氯化钾混合熔盐作为电解质，以液态金属铋作为阴极，接入阳极并进行电解；在阴极获得钠‑铋合金，在阳极获得硫单质；(4)将所得钠‑铋合金与水反应，使该合金中的钠反应得到液碱与氢气。本方法原料来源丰富且低廉，具有成本优势；工艺简单安全且无氯气生成，可减少环境污染风险；本发明可拓展至活泼金属储能间歇制氢方面，适用于放大生产，具备大规模生产潜力。"
                }
            ]
